      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPIN AROUND BLUE (2) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.3 lengths away in second (30.41) behind Malicious at Taree Super Track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can go on with it. ZIPPING DESIRE (1) is an accomplished stayer with a great record at the longer races. Finished third latest over 600m at this track (35.33) in a Grade 5. Goes very well at the journey winning one races. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Must be included in calculations. BLAZING PRINCE (5) has struggled for best form recently, last time finishing 6th (35.42) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has won here at this journey. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Can measure up this time. ZIPPING PERCAT (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
